Detailed Description

cvmx_pcsx::_log_anl_reg

PCSX Logic Analyzer Register NOTE: Logic Analyzer is enabled with LA_EN for xaui only. PKT_SZ is effective only when LA_EN=1 For normal operation(xaui), this bit must be 0. The dropped lane is used to send rxc[3:0]. See pcs.csr for sgmii/1000Base-X logic analyzer mode. For full description see document at .../rtl/pcs/readme_logic_analyzer.txt
